```plantuml
@startuml SpektraSystems_CloudLabs-Azure

actor User
participant "Azure Portal" as Portal
participant "Azure Migrate" as Migrate
participant "Hyper-V Manager" as HyperV
participant "Azure VMs" as VMs
participant "Azure Functions" as Functions
participant "Cosmos DB" as Cosmos
participant "Azure Monitor" as Monitor
participant "Log Analytics" as Logs
participant "Application Insights" as Insights

User -> Portal: Accesses Azure Portal
Portal -> Migrate: Creates Migration Project
Migrate -> HyperV: Assesses On-Prem VMs
HyperV --> Migrate: VM Assessment Data
Migrate -> VMs: Initiates Server Replication
VMs --> Migrate: Replication Status
Migrate -> VMs: Executes Test Migration
VMs --> Migrate: Migration Results
User -> Portal: Validates Migrated Server

User -> Portal: Deploys Azure Functions
Portal -> Functions: Publishes Function App
Functions -> Cosmos: Connects to Database
Cosmos --> Functions: Data Access Confirmation
User -> Portal: Configures Authentication
Portal -> Functions: Sets Up Auth Providers

User -> Portal: Configures Monitoring
Portal -> Monitor: Sets Up Alerts
Monitor -> Logs: Configures Log Collection
Logs --> Monitor: Log Data
Monitor -> Insights: Configures App Monitoring
Insights --> Monitor: Performance Data
Monitor -> Portal: Displays Dashboard

@enduml
```